      #slider2full
        label
          strong Amplitude 
          | corresponds to our perception of loudness:
        .slider-range-max.slider-2#slider-2 role="slider" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="1.5" aria-valuenow="0" aria-valuetext="" aria-orientation="horizontal"
        input.amount2.d-none readonly="readonly" type="text"
